{"id":157651,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/06/雙證雙審-陸客月底前自由行/","date":"2011-06-03T11:30:25Z","modified":"2011-12-28T23:40:54Z","title":"雙證雙審 陸客月底前自由行","content":"<p>各界期盼的陸客自由行將在6月底前開放，目前確定取消保證金制度，改採「雙證件、雙審查」，由親屬擔任保人，並提供財力證明；開放人數原則上仍是每天500人；首批開放試點城市除了北京、上海，廈門市也可望納入。至於離島小三通自由行正同步溝通中，屆時將一併開放。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://chinatimes.feedsportal.com/c/33012/f/537211/s/1598db89/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E9%9B%99%E8%AD%89%E9%9B%99%E5%AF%A9+%E9%99%B8%E5%AE%A2%E6%9C%88%E5%BA%95%E5%89%8D%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E8%A1%8C&amp;link=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.chinatimes.com%2Fmainland%2F17180503%2F112011060200209.html\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/06/260f6417emailthis2.gif.gif\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E9%9B%99%E8%AD%89%E9%9B%99%E5%AF%A9+%E9%99%B8%E5%AE%A2%E6%9C%88%E5%BA%95%E5%89%8D%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E8%A1%8C&amp;link=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.chinatimes.com%2Fmainland%2F17180503%2F112011060200209.html\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2011/06/044291a1bookmark.gif.gif\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/104456518202/u/0/f/537211/c/33012/s/1598db89/a2.htm\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/104456518202/u/0/f/537211/c/33012/s/1598db89/a2.img\" /></a></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinatimes.feedsportal.com/c/33012/f/537211/s/1598db89/mf.gif\" /></p>\n<p>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> </p>\n<p>\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[18424],"tags":[16304,15396,9625]}